quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"“Sad, ndikulumbira Qur’an (iyi) ya ulaliki (wothandiza)"
  38,2,“Koma amene sadakhulupirire ali mkudzitukumula ndi makani
  38,3,"“Kodi ndimibadwo ingati taiwononga patsogolo pawo? Adakuwa kuitana (panthawi imeneyo), koma nthawi yopulumuka idali itatha"
  38,4,"“Ndipo anadabwa atawadzera mchenjezi wochokera mwa iwo. Ndipo osakhulupirira adati: “Uyu ndiwamatsenga; ngwabodza lamkunkhuniza!”"
  38,5,“Ha! Waichita milungu yambirimbiri ija kuti ikhale Mulungu Mmodzi Yekha? Ndithu ichi nchinthu chodabwitsa.”
  38,6,"“Ndipo adanyamuka akuluakulu a mwa iwo nati: “Nyamukani muzikapitiriza kupembedza milungu yanu. Ndithu chinthu ichi (nchoipa); chikulinga ife (kuti tisiyane ndi milungu yathu).”"
  38,7,"““Sitidamve zimenezi (zakuti Mulungu Ndimmodzi ngakhale) m’chipembedzo chakale (Chikhrisitu). Ichi sikanthu, koma ndibodza lopeka.”"
  38,8,““Kodi uthengawo (wakuti Mulungu Ndimmodzi) wavumbulutsidwa kwa iye pakati pathu?” Koma iwo akukaika ndi ulaliki Wanga. Koma sadalawebe chilango Changa
  38,9,"“Kodi iwo ali nazo nkhokwe za chifundo cha Mbuye wako, Wamphamvu zoposa, Wopatsa mochuluka"
  38,10,"“Kapena ufumu wa kumwamba ndi pansi ndi zapakati pake, ngwawo. Ngati zili choncho atakwera makwelero (kuti akafike pamalo poti akalamulire zimene akufuna, ngati angathe kutero)"
  38,11,"“Awa (Aquraish kuonjezera pa kudzitama kwawo), nkagulu kochepa ndi kofooka. Kagonjetsedwa monga makamu ankhondo (omwe adagonjetsedwa kale omwe amatsutsana ndi aneneri akale)"
  38,12,"“Patsogolo pawo, anthu a Nuh, Âdi ndi Farawo, mwini nyumba zitalizitali (Pyramid), adatsutsa (aneneri awo)"
  38,13,"“Ndi Asamudu, ndi anthu a Luti ndi (anthu a Shuaib) eni mitengo yambiri yothothana, amenewo ndiwo makamu"
  38,14,“Onsewa adatsutsa atumiki; basi chilango Changa chidatsimikizika (pa iwo)
  38,15,"“Ndipo awa (Aquraish), sayembekeza china koma mkuwe umodzi wosabwereza. (Ndipo ukadzachitika, onse adzafa)"
  38,16,"“Ndipo akunena (mwachipongwe): “E Mbuye wathu! Tipatsirenitu gawo la chilango chathu lisanafike tsiku lachiwerengero.”"